headline: This Buffett favorite is one of 4 cheap stocks the ‘smartest money’ has been buying lately
summary: It’s bullish when insiders invest their own money into their companies — especially when those executives and directors have a record of savvy timing.

headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks to Own for Decades and 1 to Think Twice About
summary: While strong cash flow is a key indicator of stability, it doesn’t always translate to superior returns. Some cash-heavy businesses struggle with inefficient spending, slowing demand, or weak competitive positioning.
